docstring:
"""
    This is the basic form field for a Geometry.  Any textual input that is
    accepted by GEOSGeometry is accepted by this form.  By default,
    this includes WKT, HEXEWKB, WKB (in a buffer), and GeoJSON.
    """
name: GeometryField

methods.docstring: """Transform the value to a Geometry object."""
methods.name: to_python

methods.docstring:
"""
        Validate that the input value can be converted to a Geometry object
        and return it. Raise a ValidationError if the value cannot be
        instantiated as a Geometry.
        """
methods.name: clean

methods.docstring: """ Compare geographic value of data with its initial value. """
methods.name: has_changed
